snippet: Former partners at Dewey & LeBoeuf agreed on Thursday to return more than $60 million of their compensation to help pay the failed law firm's creditors.
abstract: Former partners at Dewey & LeBoeuf agreed on Thursday to return more than $60 million of their compensation to help pay the failed law firm's creditors.

headline.main: Former Dewey Partners to Return Millions
